cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.CL 

This paper discusses the use of dropout as a regularization technique in deep neural networks, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and neural networks (cs.NE). The paper also focuses on improving image classification performance (cs.CV) and proposes a new technique for activation functions (cs.AI) that can be applied to natural language processing tasks (cs.CL).
